title: Couple with Heart: Man, Person, Medium Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Couple with Heart: Man, Person, Medium Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic couple consisting of a man and a person, with a heart symbolizing their love and connection. The medium skin tone indicates a specific representation of the individuals.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the couple with a heart, featuring a man and a person with no skin tone and medium skin tone, radiates warmth and connection, thanks to Apple's signature 3D shading. The central heart, rendered in a vivid red, draws the eye and emphasizes their bond. This emoji on Apple devices beautifully represents diverse relationships and heartfelt affection.
